From: "copilot-swe-agent[bot]" <198982749+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Apr 2026 00:00:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add bulk workout tools (upload_workouts,
 delete_workouts, schedule_workouts)

Adds three new MCP tools for bulk workout operations:

- upload_workouts: Upload multiple workouts in a single call. Returns a
  summary with total/succeeded/failed counts and per-workout results.

- delete_workouts: Delete multiple workouts by ID in a single call.
  Returns per-workout success/failure status including HTTP status codes.

- schedule_workouts: Schedule multiple workouts to calendar dates in one
  call. Supports both existing workout IDs and inline upload-and-schedule
  (provide workout_data instead of workout_id to upload and schedule in
  one step).

Also adds:
- 16 integration tests covering single/multiple items, partial failures,
  exception handling, missing field validation, and the inline
  upload-then-schedule flow
- 5 e2e tests for all three new tools

Co-authored-by: brunosantos <495067+brunosantos@users.noreply.github.com>
